'''Digworms''' were nocturnal scavengers native to to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Kamar/Legends|Kamar]].<ref name="hsr">''[[Han Solo's Revenge]]''</ref> Their corrosive digestive juices allowed them to burrow through rock.<ref name="cswe">{{CSWECite|I|189|Digworm}}</ref>

